=== 《迪歐年代》和天堂與地獄（2006 - 2010年） ===
[[File:Tony-Iommi_2009-06-11_Chicago_photoby_Adam-Bielawski.jpg|left]]
2006年，當奧茲正在籌備製作個人專輯《{{link-en|黑雨 (專輯)|Black Rain (Ozzy Osbourne album)|黑雨}}》時，{{link-en|犀牛唱片|Rhino Entertainment}}在2007年4月3日發行了精選輯《{{link-en|黑色安息日：迪歐年代|Black Sabbath: The Dio Years}}》，從迪歐在樂團任期內參與過的四張專輯中選曲。同時東尼、吉澤、溫尼和迪歐再次合作，為此精選輯創作了三首新歌。該精選輯登上告示牌二百大專輯榜第54名<ref>{{Allmusic |class=album |id=the-dio-years-mw0000478435 |tab=awards |label="''The Dio Years'': Charts & Awards > Billboard Albums" |language = 英語|accessdate=2011-09-14}}</ref>。新曲〈{{link-en|哭泣的魔鬼|The Devil Cried}}〉登上告示牌主流搖滾單曲榜第37名<ref>{{Allmusic |class=album |id=the-dio-years-mw0000478435 |tab=awards |label="''The Dio Years'': Charts & Awards > Billboard Singles" |language = 英語|accessdate=2011-09-14}}</ref>。市場反應讓樂團非常滿意，於是東尼和迪歐便決定組成《天堂與地獄》時期的陣容，舉行{{link-en|2007天堂與地獄巡迴之旅|Heaven and Hell 2007 Tour}}<ref>{{cite news | language=en | first=Jon | last=Wiederhorn | title=Half Of Black Sabbath Reunite With Dio; Tour Begins In March | date=2006-12-15 | url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1548069/20061214/black_sabbath.jhtml | work=MTV | pages= | accessdate=2008-06-25 | deadurl=no | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080513203642/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1548069/20061214/black_sabbath.jhtml | archivedate=2008-05-13 }}</ref>。而奧茲、吉澤、東尼和比爾的陣容仍然正式稱為黑色安息日，新陣容選擇依照當年的同名專輯稱為{{link-en|天堂與地獄 (樂團)|Heaven & Hell (band)|天堂與地獄}}，以避免混淆。東尼說：「取這個名字就不會讓演唱會上的樂迷困惑，他們會明白自己不會在那裡聽到〈鋼鐵人〉或〈戰爭豬玀〉或其他的歌。這個組合代表不是奧茲時期，也不會表演老歌，所以我們稱自己為天堂和地獄，正是為了要重溫那個時期。那時候我們做了很多努力，很高興能再度和迪歐重聚」<ref name="Black Sabbath member history"/>。比爾最初預計參與精選輯新歌的錄音和巡演，最終在錄音前因音樂上的差異問題，拒絕成為樂團的鼓手<ref>{{cite web|language = en|url=http://www.blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=135471|title=Ward on Quitting Heaven & Hell: I Was Uncomfortable With Some Things Surrounding The Project|last=Russell|first=Tom|date=2010-02-20|publisher=Blabbermouth.net|accessdate=2010-02-21}}</ref>。他的位置由前鼓手溫尼取代。

2007年3月11日，天堂與地獄巡迴之旅展開，邀請[[麥加帝斯|麥加帝斯]]、{{link-en|機械頭|Machine Head (band)}}、[[上帝羔羊樂團|上帝羔羊]]、{{link-en|德國女皇 (樂團)|Queensrÿche|德國女皇}}、[[埃利斯·庫珀|埃利斯·庫珀]]、{{link-en|冰凍大地|Iced Earth}}暖場<ref>{{cite news|language = en|title=Queensryche's Geoff Tate to sing national anthem at Seahawks game|date=2007-12-12|url =http://www.seattlepi.com/pop/335313_tf213.html |work = Seattle Post-Intelligencer| accessdate = 2008-03-17}}</ref>，並於3月30日在紐約錄製了一張現場專輯和DVD，名為《{{link-en|無線電城音樂廳現場|Live from Radio City Music Hall}}》，獲金唱片認證<ref>{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.riaa.com/goldandplatinumdata.php?resultpage=1&table=SEARCH_RESULTS&action=&title=Live%20from%20Radio%20City%20Music%20Hall&artist=&format=&debutLP=&category=&sex=&releaseDate=&requestNo=&type=&level=&label=&company=&certificationDate=&awardDescription=&catalogNo=&aSex=&rec_id=&charField=&gold=&platinum=&multiPlat=&level2=&certDate=&album=&id=&after=&before=&startMonth=1&endMonth=1&startYear=1958&endYear=2009&sort=Artist&perPage=25|title=RIAA Gold & Platinum database-''Live from Radio City Music Hall''|accessdate=2009-03-04|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924153134/http://www.riaa.com/goldandplatinumdata.php?resultpage=1&table=SEARCH_RESULTS&action=&title=Live%20from%20Radio%20City%20Music%20Hall&artist=&format=&debutLP=&category=&sex=&releaseDate=&requestNo=&type=&level=&label=&company=&certificationDate=&awardDescription=&catalogNo=&aSex=&rec_id=&charField=&gold=&platinum=&multiPlat=&level2=&certDate=&album=&id=&after=&before=&startMonth=1&endMonth=1&startYear=1958&endYear=2009&sort=Artist&perPage=25|archivedate=2015-09-24}}</ref>。11月，迪歐確認該組合計劃錄製一張新的錄音室專輯<ref>{{cite web |language=en |last=Elliott |first=Mike |url=http://www.komodorock.com/interviews/interviews/komodo-rock-talks-with-ronnie-james-dio-200711012460/ |title=Komodo Rock Talks With Ronnie James Dio |publisher=Komodorock.com |accessdate=2008-04-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080320074153/http://www.komodorock.com/interviews/interviews/komodo-rock-talks-with-ronnie-james-dio-200711012460/ |archivedate=2008-03-20 }}</ref>。2008年7月，黑色安息日推出典藏套裝合輯《{{link-en|地獄的規則|The Rules of Hell}}》，包含所有迪歐時期的作品<ref>{{cite news | language=en | first=Jim | last=Welte | title=Legends align for Metal Masters Tour | date=2008-04-22 | url=http://www.mp3.com/news/stories/11191.html | work=MP3.com | accessdate=2008-04-23 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080424114144/http://www.mp3.com/news/stories/11191.html | archivedate=2008-04-24 }}</ref>。8月，他們與猶大祭司、摩托頭、[[Testament|聖約]]一起舉行了{{link-en|金屬大師巡迴之旅|Metal Masters Tour}}<ref>{{cite web|language = en|url=http://www.blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=95359 |title=JUDAS PRIEST Frontman On 'Metal Masters' Tour: 'We Insisted On A Classic Metal Package' |publisher=Blabbermouth.net |accessdate=2008-04-25}}</ref>。2009年4月28日，天堂與地獄發行了新專輯《{{link-en|小心魔鬼就在你身邊|The Devil You Know (Heaven & Hell album)}}》<ref name=billb09>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/269438/heaven-hell-feeling-devilish-on-new-album |title=Heaven & Hell Feeling Devilish on New Album |accessdate=2009-02-13 |last=Cohen |first=Jonathan |date=2009-02-10 |work=Billboard |publisher=Howard Appelbaum |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130607033128/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/269438/heaven-hell-feeling-devilish-on-new-album |archivedate=2013-06-07 }}</ref>，登上美國榜第8名<ref>{{cite news|language=en|url=http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=119520|title=Heaven & Hell's 'The Devil You Know' Lands in U.S. Top 10|date=2009-05-06|work=Blabbermouth.net|publisher=Roadrunner Records|accessdate=2009-05-06|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/67TJ3IEQ8?url=http://legacy.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article|archivedate=2012-05-07}}</ref>。迪歐說：「這些歌曲錄製後，我想離開天堂與地獄，回到我自己的樂團。和黑色安息日再做張專輯，是我心中最後一件想做的事了」<ref>{{cite news | language=en | first=J. | last=Bennett | title=RONNIE JAMES DIO: 'The Last Thing On My Mind Is Doing Another BLACK SABBATH Album' | date=2007-06-27 | url=http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=75635 | work=blabbermouth.net | accessdate=2009-03-08 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090617020717/http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=75635 | archivedate=2009-06-17 }}</ref>。Allmusic表示：「這張專輯有如黑色安息日的《偏執狂》，天堂與地獄展現了不同的音樂性，取不同的團名是合適的」<ref>{{cite web|language = en|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/r1538717|title=The Devil You Know – Heaven & Hell|publisher=Allmusic|first=Phil|last=Freeman|accessdate=2012-04-26}}</ref>。英國重金屬雜誌《{{link-en|金屬之鎚|Metal Hammer}}》將這張專輯描述為「本年度的重量級新作之一」<ref name='metalhammerreview'>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.metalhammer.co.uk/news/track-by-track-heaven-and-hell-the-devil-you-know/ |title=Track-By-Track: Heaven And Hell – The Devil You Know |accessdate=2009-03-30 |date=2009-03-30 |work={{link-en|金屬之鎚|Metal Hammer}} |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/67TJ75fwb?url=http://www.metalhammer.co.uk/news/track-by-track-heaven-and-hell-the-devil-you-know/ |archivedate=2012-05-07 }}</ref>。

2009年5月，奧茲在紐約聯邦法院控告東尼未經許可及非法使用黑色安息日的註冊商標，使其版權在[[美國專利及商標局|美國專利及商標局]]登記名字為東尼·艾歐密一人所有，而非黑色安息日當年的創始成員平均獲得樂團名字的使用權。奧茲要求東尼付出樂團商標等有關一切的50%利潤。奧茲表示「我對於最後要用法律去解決我跟東尼的問題，感到非常..非常的遺憾。但經過三年無數次的妥協，我已經沒得選了。東尼，做你正確的決定吧」<ref name="MusicMight"/>。東尼則說：「我是黑色安息日41年裡唯一不變的樂團成員，其他成員在80年代就紛紛退出，放棄了這支樂團，因此我對樂團名稱有更多的權利」<ref>{{cite web|language=en|last=Harris|first=Chris|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/ozzy-osbourne-suing-tony-iommi-for-black-sabbath-name-20090529|title=Ozzy Osbourne Suing Tony Iommi For Black Sabbath Name|work=Rolling Stone|date=2009-05-29|accessdate=2013-02-10|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130202160108/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/ozzy-osbourne-suing-tony-iommi-for-black-sabbath-name-20090529|archivedate=2013-02-02}}</ref>。11月25日，迪歐被診斷出罹患[[胃癌|胃癌]]，並到[[德州大學安德森癌症中心|德州大學安德森癌症中心]]接受治療<ref>{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.brooklynvegan.com/archives/2009/11/ronnie_james_di.html|title=Dio Has Stomach Cancer|work=Brooklyn Vegan|accessdate=2010-07-24|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100520013458/http://www.brooklynvegan.com/archives/2009/11/ronnie_james_di.html|archivedate=2010-05-20}}</ref>。天堂與地獄原本計畫在迪歐休養後進一步開始活動，在歐洲與[[鐵娘子樂團|鐵娘子]]巡演，但後來由於迪歐健康狀況惡化，取消所有計畫。

2010年4月17日，黑色安息日與金屬製品合作發行限量版單曲，以慶祝{{link-en|世界唱片行日|Record Store Day}}<ref>{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.idiomag.com/peek/108571/black_sabbath|title=News: Black Sabbath and Metallica to issue limited edition split single|accessdate=2010-04-06|publisher={{link-en|idiomag|idiomag}}|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120120131152/http://www.idiomag.com/peek/108571/black_sabbath|archivedate=2012-01-20}}</ref>。5月16日上午，迪歐因胃癌逝世，享壽六十七歲<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.blogs.cnn.com/2010/05/16/metal-rocker-ronnie-james-dio-has-died-wife-says/ |title=CNN.com: Metal rocker Ronnie James Dio has died, wife says |publisher=News.blogs.cnn.com |date=2010-05-16 |accessdate=2010-11-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100909043635/http://news.blogs.cnn.com/2010/05/16/metal-rocker-ronnie-james-dio-has-died-wife-says/ |archivedate=2010-09-09 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|language=en|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/8685851.stm|title=Heavy metal singer Ronnie James Dio dies at 67|publisher=BBC News|date=2010-05-16|accessdate=2013-02-09|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130417233051/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/8685851.stm|archivedate=2013-04-17}}</ref>。6月，奧茲和東尼的商標訴訟官司結束，但並未公開和解的詳細資訊<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.classicrockmagazine.com/news/ozzy-and-iommi-settle-sabbath-legal-battle/ |title=Ozzy And Iommi Settle Sabbath Legal Battle |date=2010-06-05 |publisher={{link-en|Classic Rock|Classic Rock (magazine)}} |accessdate=2010-06-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100610224542/http://www.classicrockmagazine.com/news/ozzy-and-iommi-settle-sabbath-legal-battle |archivedate=2010-06-10 }}</ref>。

