=== 原始陣容團聚與《十三》（2010 - 2014年） ===

2010年1月奧茲在宣傳自傳新書《{{link-en|我是奧茲|I Am Ozzy}}》的採訪中表示：「雖然我不排除，但我仍懷疑黑色安息日所有四個原創成員還會團聚的可能性。我的意思不是永遠，但現在我不覺得有任何機會。誰知道未來對我有什麼好處？如果這是我的命運，那也罷了」<ref>{{cite news|language=en|title=Ozzy: Sabbath not regrouping|date=2010-01-25|agency=Associated Press|url=http://jam.canoe.ca/Music/2010/01/25/12611346-wenn-story.html|work=Canoe|accessdate=2010-01-25|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100129000310/http://jam.canoe.ca/Music/2010/01/25/12611346-wenn-story.html|archivedate=2010-01-29}}</ref>。7月，吉澤表示：「2011年將不會有黑色安息日的團聚，因為奧茲已經承諾要舉行他的個人巡演了」<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.metalhammer.co.uk/news/geezer-butler-no-black-sabbath-reunion-in-2011/ |title=Blog Archive " Geezer Butler: No Black Sabbath Reunion In 2011 |publisher=Metal Hammer |date=2010-12-10 |accessdate=2011-07-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110520042901/http://www.metalhammer.co.uk/news/geezer-butler-no-black-sabbath-reunion-in-2011/ |archivedate=2011-05-20 }}</ref>。然而，8月份時四名成員聚集在一起工作，並持續練團<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=921243007921360&id=109213359124333 |title=Bill Ward – Bill addresses Ozzy's Facebook post. 1. You... |publisher=Facebook |accessdate=2016-01-18 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160609000734/https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=921243007921360&id=109213359124333 |archivedate=2016-06-09 }}</ref>。

2011年11月11日，比爾、吉澤、奧茲、東尼在洛杉磯{{link-en|威士忌搖擺舞|Whisky a Go Go}}酒吧宣布他們正在錄製新專輯，並會於2012年展開宣傳巡演<ref>{{cite news|language=en|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-15705500|title=Veteran rockers Black Sabbath announce reunion|publisher=BBC News|date=2012-11-12|accessdate=2013-02-09|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130420035309/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-15705500|archivedate=2013-04-20}}</ref>。2012年1月9日，東尼被診斷出罹患[[淋巴瘤|淋巴瘤]]，樂團取消之前預訂的歐洲巡迴之旅，但仍照計畫參加了{{link-en|下載音樂節|Download Festival}}和[[Lollapalooza|羅拉帕羅扎音樂節]]<ref>{{cite news|language=en|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-birmingham-16474807|title=Tony Iommi to undergo treatment for lymphoma|publisher=BBC News|date=2012-01-09|accessdate=2013-02-09|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130420035305/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-birmingham-16474807|archivedate=2013-04-20}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|language=en|last=Greene|first=Andy|title=Black Sabbath's Tony Iommi: 'I've Had the Last Dose of Chemotherapy'|work=Rolling Stone|date=2012-03-27|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/black-sabbaths-tony-iommi-ive-had-the-last-dose-of-chemotherapy-20120327|accessdate=2013-02-09|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130202081658/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/black-sabbaths-tony-iommi-ive-had-the-last-dose-of-chemotherapy-20120327|archivedate=2013-02-02}}</ref>。樂團後來宣布，將在家鄉伯明罕演出，這是自「團圓世界巡迴之旅」後的第一場演唱會<ref>{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.metaltraveller.com/en/gigs/black_sabbath/birmingham_2012.html|title=Black Sabbath reunion concert|publisher=Metal Traveller|date=2012-05-21|accessdate=2012-05-22|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120825020434/http://www.metaltraveller.com/en/gigs/black_sabbath/birmingham_2012.html|archivedate=2012-08-25}}</ref>。2012年2月，比爾宣布他將不再參加樂團的團聚，直到他獲得「合約」<ref>{{cite news|language=en|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-16867216|title=Black Sabbath Bill Ward drummer delays band reunion|publisher=BBC News|date=2012-0-03|accessdate=2013-02-09|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120608030942/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-16867216|archivedate=2012-06-08}}</ref>。第二天，其他成員表示他們「沒得選擇，只能在沒有比爾的情況下繼續錄音」，但也說「我們的門永遠開著，希望比爾能回來」<ref>{{cite web| language = en| last = Greene| first = Andy| title = Black Sabbath Pledge To Carry on Without Drummer Bill Ward| work = Rolling Stone| publisher = Wenner Media| date = 2012-02-03| url = http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/black-sabbath-pledge-to-carry-on-without-drummer-bill-ward-20120203| accessdate = 2013-01-13| deadurl = no| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130202053227/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/black-sabbath-pledge-to-carry-on-without-drummer-bill-ward-20120203| archivedate = 2013-02-02}}</ref>。

2012年5月21日，黑色安息日在{{link-en|伯明罕O2學院|O2 Academy Birmingham}}演出，取代比爾上場的是奧茲的鼓手{{link-en|湯米·克魯弗托斯|Tommy Clufetos}}<ref>{{cite news|language=en|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/18145654|title=Reunited Black Sabbath play Birmingham gig|publisher=BBC News|date=2012-05-21|accessdate=2013-02-09|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130504010205/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/18145654|archivedate=2013-05-04}}</ref>。6月，樂團在下載音樂節登台演出，隨後在芝加哥羅拉帕羅扎音樂節表演<ref>{{cite web|language=en|last=Crookes|first=Del|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/18391342|title=Black Sabbath and Soundgarden close Download festival|publisher=BBC News|date=2012-06-11|accessdate=2013-02-09|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130617061330/http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/18391342|archivedate=2013-06-17}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|language=en|last=Kot|first=Greg|url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/music/turnitup/chi-lollapalooza-day-1-lollapalooza-opening-day-reviewed-20120803,0,1929815.column|title=Lollapalooza Day 1: Black Sabbath, Black Keys and Passion Pit's black thoughts|work=[[芝加哥論壇報|芝加哥論壇報]]|date=2012-08-04|accessdate=2013-02-09|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130209233353/http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/music/turnitup/chi-lollapalooza-day-1-lollapalooza-opening-day-reviewed-20120803,0,1929815.column|archivedate=2013-02-09}}</ref>。當月月底，樂團開始錄製新專輯<ref>{{cite web|language=en|url=https://twitter.com/GZRMusic/status/237598810912718848|title=Geezer Butler at Twitter|publisher=Twitter|date=2012-08-20|accessdate=2013-02-09|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203031735/https://twitter.com/GZRMusic/status/237598810912718848|archivedate=2013-12-03}}</ref>。
[[File:Black_Sabbath_Barclays_Center_March_2014.jpg|left]]
2013年1月13日，樂團宣布該專輯名為《十三》，並將於6月發行，鼓手為[[討伐體制樂團|討伐體制]]的{{link-en|布萊德·威克|Brad Wilk}}，製作人為瑞克·魯賓<ref>{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/black-sabbath-announce-new-album-13-due-out-in-june-20130113|title=Black Sabbath Announce New Album, '13,' Due Out in June|work=Rolling Stone|date=2013-01-13|accessdate=2013-02-09|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130202070327/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/black-sabbath-announce-new-album-13-due-out-in-june-20130113|archivedate=2013-02-02}}</ref>。2月進入專輯混音階段<ref>{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=185651|title=Black Sabbath To Begin Mixing New Album in February|publisher=Blabbermouth.net|date=2013-01-31|accessdate=2013-02-09|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130204001901/http://www.blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=185651|archivedate=2013-02-04}}</ref>。4月12日，樂團公布了專輯的曲目列表。該專輯的普通版有八首新曲，豪華版加收三首特別贈送曲<ref>{{cite web|language=en|url=http://ultimateclassicrock.com/black-sabbath-bonus-songs-13-deluxe-edition/|title=Black Sabbath Adds Bonus Songs To '13' Deluxe Edition|first=Dave|last=Lifton|publisher=Ultimate Classic Rock|date=2013-04-19|accessdate=2013-04-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130421004741/http://ultimateclassicrock.com/black-sabbath-bonus-songs-13-deluxe-edition/|archivedate=2013-04-21}}</ref>。4月19日，發行新單曲〈{{link-en|上帝已死？ (黑色安息日的歌曲)|God Is Dead?|上帝已死？}}〉<ref>{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/review/1558856/black-sabbath-god-is-dead-single-review|title=Black Sabbath, 'God Is Dead?': Single Review|first=Gary|last=Graff|work=Billboard|date=2013-04-19|accessdate=2013-04-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130422143213/http://www.billboard.com/articles/review/1558856/black-sabbath-god-is-dead-single-review|archivedate=2013-04-22}}</ref>，登上英國搖滾單曲榜第6名<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.officialcharts.com/archive-chart/_/10/2013-05-04/ |title=2013-05-04 Top 40 Rock & Metal Singles Archive |publisher=Official Charts |date=2013-05-04 |accessdate=2013-05-13 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130905061635/http://www.officialcharts.com/archive-chart/_/10/2013-05-04/ |archivedate=2013-09-05 }}</ref>。4月20日，黑色安息日展開紐澳美加巡迴之旅<ref>{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/black-sabbath-book-four-north-american-dates-20130416|title=Black Sabbath Book Four North American Dates|first=Eric D.|last=Dandton|work=Rolling Stone|date=2013-04-16|accessdate=2013-04-16|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130419043331/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/black-sabbath-book-four-north-american-dates-20130416|archivedate=2013-04-19}}</ref>。5月15日，黑色安息日的三位成員在《[[CSI犯罪現場|CSI犯罪現場]]》第十三季完結篇中客串演出，在劇中開頭演唱第二支單曲〈結局的開端〉，並有奧茲在後台與主要角色的對話<ref name="CSI"/>。影集的製片人{{link-en|唐·麥吉爾|Don McGill}}說：「當我們第一次聽說黑色安息日有興趣在專輯中創作一首關於CSI的歌曲時，我們都非常興奮，我們劇組很多人都是資深樂迷。看到這張專輯名為《十三》，而這是CSI第十三季的結局，它似乎是一個完美的搭配。對此，我們全都非常激動」<ref name="CSI">{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/black-sabbath-to-premiere-new-single-on-csi-season-finale-20130410|title=Black Sabbath to Premiere New Single on 'CSI' Season Finale|work=Rolling Stone|first=Andy|last=Greene|date=2013-04-10|accessdate=2013-04-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130413010105/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/black-sabbath-to-premiere-new-single-on-csi-season-finale-20130410|archivedate=2013-04-13}}</ref>。

6月10日，樂團發行第十九張專輯《{{link-en|十三 (黑色安息日的專輯)|13 (Black Sabbath album)|十三}}》，它榮登美國<ref name="BLACK SABBATH13200">{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.billboard.com/artist/288497/Black+Sabbath/chart?f=305 |title=Black Sabbath |publisher=billboard |date=2013-06-29 |accessdate=2013-09-13 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130617115731/http://www.billboard.com/artist/288497/black%2Bsabbath/chart?f=305 |archivedate=2013-06-17 }}</ref>、英國<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.officialcharts.com/artist/14136/black%20sabbath/ |title=Black Sabbath |publisher=Official Charts Company |date=2013-06-16 |accessdate=2013-09-13 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161009065156/http://www.officialcharts.com/artist/14136/black%20sabbath/ |archivedate=2016-10-09 }}</ref>、瑞士<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.swisscharts.com/album/Black-Sabbath/13-211350 |title=BLACK SABBATH - 13 |publisher=Swiss Charts |date=2013-06-16 |accessdate=2013-09-13 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140330125009/http://swisscharts.com/album/Black-Sabbath/13-211350 |archivedate=2014-03-30 }}</ref>、瑞典<ref>{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.swedishcharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Black+Sabbath&titel=13&cat=a|title=BLACK SABBATH - 13|publisher=Swedishcharts|date=2013-06-16|accessdate=2013-09-13|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131109032259/http://swedishcharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Black+Sabbath&titel=13&cat=a|archivedate=2013-11-09}}</ref>、挪威<ref>{{cite web |language = en|url=http://www.norwegiancharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Black+Sabbath&titel=13&cat|title=BLACK SABBATH - 13|publisher=Norwegiancharts |date=2013-06-16 |accessdate=2013-09-13}}</ref>、紐西蘭<ref>{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.charts.org.nz/showitem.asp?interpret=Black+Sabbath&titel=13&cat=a|title=BLACK SABBATH - 13|publisher=NEW ZEALAND CHARTS|date=2013-06-16|accessdate=2013-09-13|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130917065319/http://charts.org.nz/showitem.asp?interpret=Black+Sabbath&titel=13&cat=a|archivedate=2013-09-17}}</ref>、德國<ref>{{cite web|language=de|url=http://musicline.de/de/chartverfolgung_summary/artist/Black+Sabbath/?type=longplay|title=BLACK SABBATH - 13|publisher=Musicline|date=2013-06-16|accessdate=2013-09-13|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303210111/http://musicline.de/de/chartverfolgung_summary/artist/Black+Sabbath/?type=longplay|archivedate=2016-03-03}}</ref>、丹麥<ref>{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.danishcharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Black+Sabbath&titel=13&cat=a|title=BLACK SABBATH - 13|publisher=Danish charts|date=2013-06-16|accessdate=2013-09-13|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014203001/http://danishcharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Black+Sabbath&titel=13&cat=a|archivedate=2013-10-14}}</ref>、加拿大<ref name="BLACK SABBATH13200"/>等國專輯排行榜的冠軍。該專輯獲得大部分的好評，AllMusic表示：「意想不到的精彩，天啟的專輯，是任何一位死忠硬搖滾或金屬迷都必需擁有的作品」<ref>{{cite web|language = en|last=Thomas |first=Fred |url={{Allmusic|class=album |id=13-mw0002480471 |pure_url=yes}} |title=13 - Black Sabbath |publisher=AllMusic |accessdate=2015-01-13}}</ref>。《金屬之鎚》雜誌認為：「我們可以從黑色安息日的發展中，觀察到重金屬音樂形成的歷史，並得出結論，樂團的經典陣容證明了他們與現代音樂具有重要的關聯」<ref>{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.metalhammer.co.uk/news/review-black-sabbath-13-yep-thats-the-full-new-black-sabbath-album-reviewed-right-here/|title=Black Sabbath '13' Review|publisher=金屬之鎚|date=2013-05-28|accessdate=2013-06-04|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130607063301/http://www.metalhammer.co.uk/news/review-black-sabbath-13-yep-thats-the-full-new-black-sabbath-album-reviewed-right-here/|archivedate=2013-06-07}}</ref>。

7月，黑色安息日抵達北美洲繼續巡迴之旅（自2001年7月以來的第一次），10月進行南美洲之旅，11月則是歐洲之旅，一直演出到12月。途中，東尼獲英國[[考文垂大學|考文垂大學]]授予藝術博士榮譽學位，校方表示：「東尼身為重金屬音樂的創始人、以及業界最有影響力的人物之一，我們希望藉由學位來表彰他對流行音樂世界的貢獻」<ref>{{cite news|language=en|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-24921081|title=Black Sabbath's Tony Iommi in Coventry University degree honour|date=2013-11-12|website=[[英國廣播公司新聞|英國廣播公司新聞]]|accessdate=2017-02-12|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170213005332/http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-24921081|archivedate=2017-02-13}}</ref>。11月13日，樂團榮獲{{link-en|經典搖滾獎|Classic Rock Roll of Honour Awards}}「年度最佳專輯」、「年度勁爆大事」以及「當世傳奇」等三項大獎<ref>{{cite news|url=https://anntw.com/articles/20131117-a2Za|title=老樂團黑色安息日 獲經典搖滾獎|date=2013-11-17|website=台灣醒報 wiki|accessdate=2017-02-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170219133039/https://anntw.com/articles/20131117-a2Za|archivedate=2017-02-19}}</ref>。2014年1月26日，樂團憑藉單曲〈上帝已死？〉第二次拿下[[第56屆葛萊美獎|第56屆葛萊美獎]]「最佳金屬樂演奏獎」<ref name="Grammy2014">{{cite news|language=en|url=http://loudwire.com/black-sabbath-god-is-dead-wins-2014-grammy-best-metal-performance/|title=Black Sabbath's 'God Is Dead?' Wins 2014 Grammy for Best Metal Performance|last=Childers|first=Chad|date=2014-01-26|website={{link-en|Loudwire|Loudwire}}|accessdate=2014-01-26|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140128223725/http://loudwire.com/black-sabbath-god-is-dead-wins-2014-grammy-best-metal-performance/|archivedate=2014-01-28}}</ref>。3至4月，樂團再回到北美巡演，6月重返歐洲，在英國倫敦結束巡迴<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://loudwire.com/black-sabbath-announce-2014-north-american-tour-dates/ |title=Black Sabbath Announce 2014 North American Tour Dates |publisher=Loudwire.com |date=2013-11-14 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2016-01-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113192940/http://loudwire.com/black-sabbath-announce-2014-north-american-tour-dates/ |archivedate=2016-01-13 }}</ref>。

